                  </div>
                  <span class="">文明的冲突：
 </span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/18084911/">(<span class="">2回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-05-02 12:26</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">5人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                文明的冲突：
<div class="left"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p18084911-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

